From 5839646fb82549504f91f88a479deb6ce9de2158 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tony Murray <murraytony@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 1 Mar 2026 16:21:19 -0600
Subject: [PATCH] Remove netcmd ajax (#19131)

* Remove netcmd ajax
Unfixable security vulnerabilites and little value.

* Remove unused binary settings
